 Amnesty International, &#8220;Violence is Not Just a Family Affair: Women Face Abuse in Tajikistan&#8221; 
</p>
<p>(London, 2009) (available from www.amnesty.org/en/library/asset/EUR60/001/2009/en/59bb6e9b-
