 <i>Domestic Violence in Tajikistan</i> (Minneapolis, The Advocates for Human Rights, 2008) (available 
</p>
<p>from www.stopvaw.org/uploads/tajikistan_3_6_07_layout_-_final_mc.pdf), p. 46. See also Amnesty 
International, &#8220;Violence is Not Just a Family Affair&#8221; (see footnote 81), p. 25. 
